<D>__{the song. are you sincere with me, fredo?}
<C>__{fredo}
<D>__{sincere. what are you talking about, of course i'm sincere with you, mike.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{then i'm going to confide in you; trust you with something.}
<C>__{fredo}
<P>__{(sicilian)}
<D>__{mike, are you crazy, i'm your brother.}
<C>__{michael}
<D>__{tonight we've been invited to a reception at the presidential palace; to bring in the new year. you and i will go in a special car that's being sent. they'll have cocktails... then dinner, and a reception with the president. when it's over, it will be suggested that you take questadt and his friends from washington to spend the night with some women. i will go home alone in the car; and before i reach the hotel, i will be assassinated.}
<C>__{fredo}
